1 E. The Department of Environmental Quality may, after notice
2 and opportunity for a hearing pursuant to the Administrative
3 Procedures Act, assess administrative penalties and may revoke,
4 suspend, or deny renewal of a certification pursuant to Section 2-3-
5 502 of Title 27A of the Oklahoma Statutes for any violation of this
6 section or rules promulgated pursuant thereto. Such administrative
7 penalties shall be deposited as provided in Section 2-3-401 of Title
8 27A of the Oklahoma Statutes.
9 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
